NOTICE
======

SC4PIM-X was originally created by wouanagaine (circa 2009) as a plugin
manager and lot editor for SimCity 4. It was written in Python 2.4 and
distributed only as compiled bytecode.

The original source code was lost, after which the tool could no longer be
maintained by its author. wouanagaine never published the SC4PIM source code
and never attached a license to it. Copyright in the original work therefore
remains with wouanagaine, and all rights are reserved.

This repository is an unofficial community decompilation and Python 3
modernization of SC4PIM-X, created and shared in good faith for the
preservation and continued use of an abandoned SimCity 4 community tool. It is
not affiliated with, or endorsed by, EA/Maxis or the original author.

No formal license has been granted for this code. It is provided as-is, with
no warranty of any kind. If you are the rights holder (or act on their behalf)
and would like this repository changed or taken down, please open an issue and
the maintainers will comply.

For reference, wouanagaine did deliberately release a different tool of his,
SC4Mapper, under a permissive BSD-style license
(https://github.com/caspervg/SC4Mapper-2013). That reflects his general
openness toward his SimCity 4 tools, but it is NOT a license for SC4PIM and
does not apply to this repository.
